---
title: Onze behandelingen — Fysiopraktijk Zeist
description: Overzicht van alle behandelingen bij Fysiopraktijk Zeist. Fysiotherapie, manuele therapie, dry needling, echografie, FysioFitness, valpreventie, handtherapie en voetentraining.
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block page_styles %}
  <style>
    /* Hero */
    .page-hero { background: var(--teal); padding: 56px 0 52px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .page-hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px; pointer-events: none; }
    .page-hero__inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .breadcrumb { font-size: .8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); }
    .breadcrumb a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .page-hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.15; }
    .page-hero p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); max-width: 580px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .page-hero__badges { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
    .badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2); border-radius: 50px; padding: 6px 14px; font-size: .8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.9); font-weight: 500; }
    /* Diensten grid */
    .diensten-section { padding: 72px 0; }
    .diensten-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 48px; }
    .dienst-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--gray-light); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 32px 28px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; transition: all .25s ease; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    .dienst-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal-light); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .dienst-card__icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px; background: var(--teal-pale); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .dienst-card__label { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--orange); }
    .dienst-card h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.25; }
    .dienst-card p { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.65; flex: 1; }
    .dienst-card__link { font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--teal); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .dienst-card:hover .dienst-card__link { text-decoration: underline; }
    /* Klachten banner */
    .klachten-banner { background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-light); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light); padding: 56px 0; }
    .klachten-banner__inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; }
    .klachten-banner h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .klachten-banner p { color: var(--gray); font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .klachten-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .klacht-tag { background: var(--teal-pale); color: var(--teal); border-radius: 50px; padding: 6px 14px; font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 500; }
    /* CTA sectie */
    .cta-section { background: var(--teal); padding: 72px 0; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .cta-section p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.75); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 32px; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .btn-group { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    @media (max-width: 900px) { .klachten-banner__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .diensten-section { padding: 48px 0; } .diensten-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<!-- Hero -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container page-hero__inner">
    <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › Behandelingen</p>
    <h1>Onze behandelingen</h1>
    <p>Van fysiotherapie en manuele therapie tot dry needling, echografie en FysioFitness — alles onder één dak. Meestal geen verwijzing nodig.</p>
    <div class="page-hero__badges">
      <span class="badge">✓ Meestal geen verwijzing nodig</span>
      <span class="badge">✓ Binnen 2 dagen geholpen</span>
      <span class="badge">✓ {{ general.review_score }}/10 beoordeling</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Diensten overzicht -->
<section class="diensten-section">
  <div class="container">
    <span style="font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange)">Wat wij doen</span>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:6px">{{ services.items | length }} gespecialiseerde behandelingen</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--gray);font-size:.95rem;max-width:560px;line-height:1.7">Elk met een eigen specialist in ons team. Samen meer dan 100 jaar klinische ervaring.</p>
    <div class="diensten-grid">
      {% for dienst in services.items %}
      <a href="{{ dienst.url if dienst.url else '#' }}" class="dienst-card">
        <div class="dienst-card__icon">{{ dienst.icon }}</div>
        <span class="dienst-card__label">Behandeling</span>
        <h2>{{ dienst.name }}</h2>
        <p>{{ dienst.description }}</p>
        {% if dienst.url %}
        <span class="dienst-card__link">Meer over {{ dienst.name }} →</span>
        {% endif %}
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Klachten banner -->
<section class="klachten-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="klachten-banner__inner">
      <div>
        <h2>Herkent u één van deze klachten?</h2>
        <p>Dan bent u bij ons aan het goede adres. U kunt direct bellen of een afspraak maken — zonder verwijzing van de huisarts.</p>
        <a href="/#afspraak" class="btn btn-primary">Maak een afspraak</a>
      </div>
      <div class="klachten-list">
        {% for item in complaints.items %}
        <span class="klacht-tag">{{ item.icon }} {{ item.name }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Niet zeker welke behandeling bij u past?</h2>
    <p>Bel of app ons. Wij helpen u verder en plannen de juiste therapeut voor u in.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="/#afspraak" class="btn btn-primary">📅 Afspraak maken</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/{{ general.whatsapp }}" class="btn btn-white" style="background:#fff;color:var(--teal);border-color:#fff">💬 WhatsApp ons</a>
      <a href="tel:{{ general.phone }}" class="btn btn-ghost">📞 {{ general.phone }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
